---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Privacy Policy | Complete Health Peptides"
  description="Our privacy policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our website and services."
>
  <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-700 to-secondary-700 text-white py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-heading font-bold mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-xl max-w-3xl">Learn how we handle your personal information and protect your privacy.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm p-8 mb-8">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="mb-8">Our full privacy policy is available in our documentation center. Please click the button below to view the complete policy.</p>
        
        <div class="flex justify-center my-8">
          <a 
            href="https://docs.chpeptides.com/legal/privacy-policy.html" 
            target="_blank" 
            rel="noopener noreferrer" 
            class="bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-md font-medium text-lg transition inline-flex items-center"
          >
            View Full Privacy Policy
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 ml-2" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 5.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L12.586 11H5a1 1 0 110-2h7.586l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        
        <h2>Overview</h2>
        <p>At Complete Health Peptides, we respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. This privacy policy will inform you about how we look after your personal data when you visit our website and tell you about your privacy rights and how the law protects you.</p>
        
        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We may collect, use, store and transfer different kinds of personal data about you including:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Identity Data: includes name, username or similar identifier</li>
          <li>Contact Data: includes billing address, delivery address, email address and telephone numbers</li>
          <li>Financial Data: includes payment card details</li>
          <li>Transaction Data: includes details about payments to and from you and other details of products you have purchased from us</li>
          <li>Technical Data: includes internet protocol (IP) address, your login data, browser type and version</li>
        </ul>
        
        <div class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-lg my-8">
          <p class="font-semibold">For the complete details of our privacy policy, please refer to our documentation center by clicking the button above.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>